I love this locally owned restaurant, my parents used to bring me here as a kid. Now I continue to come with and without them. I've tried several different platters throughout the years but my personal favorites are the tamales and the (taquitos) small tacos, they're both only $1.50 each. I took some pictures of the plates that I've tried and love and posted them up there.

Disgusting. I heard bad things about this place but I decided to give it a try. I stopped by in a hurry and got a chicken salad to go. It was $11.00, and when I opened it at home the lettuce was old the chicken looked old, soggy and it tasted just as bad. I dont know how you can screw up a salad and charge $11.00 for it. No passion in what they serve.. Ripoff.
